data.description: Motivated Seller! Beautifully updated “move-in ready” home complete with new roof, windows, flooring, heating/AC, water heater, kitchen countertops, and appliances! Conveniently located across from Opportunity Elementary. There are 3 bedrooms on the main floor. The Primary bedroom also has its own ¾ bathroom not typical for this era of home. Plenty of room for everyone with a second family room area complete with gas fireplace and French doors leading to 4 th bedroom. Fenced backyard with covered patio, 10x12 storage shed, and pond/waterfall feature makes this a nice place to entertain or your own quiet oasis. Take advantage of the drop with interest rates and make this your home today!
